<?php include_once ($_SERVER["DOCUMENT_ROOT"]."/header.php"); ?><div class="root container responsivegrid">  <div class="" id="page">     <div class="container-wrapper">                             <div id="container-a61c81fffd" class="cmp-container">                  <div class="container responsivegrid">  <div class="pt-large pb-small">     <div class="container-wrapper main-container">                             <div id="container-a2a2fe5fa1" class="cmp-container">                  <div class="grid"><div class="grid-component">                                            <div class="column-container  two-columns-66-33  inverted">                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="title">        <div class="title-component">     <h1 class="h1 text-left">         Turbo and Super Turbo Poker     </h1> </div> </div>                 <div class="large-to-small-fonts">       <div class="large-to-small-fonts-component">         <div class="font-size-changer-con clear">             <span class="font-size-title">Font Size</span>             <div class="font-size-changer-sizes-con">                 <span class="font-size-changer small-font-size js-small-font-size">A</span>                 <span class="font-size-changer medium-font-size js-medium-font-size selected-font-size">A</span>                 <span class="font-size-changer large-font-size js-large-font-size">A</span>             </div>         </div>     </div>      </div>                 <div class="image">           <div class="image-component img-100% None None">       <div class="image-container js-modal-open modal-enabled">                               <picture>                  <img src="/img/Turbo-1636994928656_tcm1488-537208.jpg" width="1200" height="675" alt="Turbo-1636994928656_tcm1488-537208" loading="lazy">     </picture>       </div>                        <div class="modal js-modal js-modal-close">                <div class="modal-dialog">                     <div class="modal-content js-modal-content">                          <button class="button-close js-modal-button" title="Close (Esc)" aria-label="Close (Esc)">×</button>                                              <picture>                  <img class="modal-image js-modal-image" src="/img/Turbo-1636994928656_tcm1488-537208.jpg" width="1200" height="675" alt="Turbo-1636994928656_tcm1488-537208" loading="lazy">     </picture>                      </div>                </div>           </div>       </div> </div>                 <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component None None">     <div class="text"><p>Turbo and Super Turbo tournaments are exactly as they sound and play out quite a bit faster than regular <a href="/poker-tournaments/">poker tournaments</a>. The blind levels go up rapidly throughout the game, easily whipping through large field tournaments in just a few hours. Turbo tournaments generally have blind levels of 4-6 minutes, while Super Turbo tournaments usually have levels lasting 3 minutes or even less.</p></div> </div></div>                 <div class="grid"><div class="grid-component">                                                      <div class="column-container  two-columns-50">                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="image">           <div class="image-component img-100% None None">       <div class="image-container js-modal-open modal-enabled">                               <picture>                  <img src="/img/1200x675-TS-19609-SEO-TurboPoker_Screenshot_1446113490252_tcm1488-262466.jpg" width="1200" height="675" alt="Turbo Poker" loading="lazy">     </picture>       </div>                        <div class="modal js-modal js-modal-close">                <div class="modal-dialog">                     <div class="modal-content js-modal-content">                          <button class="button-close js-modal-button" title="Close (Esc)" aria-label="Close (Esc)">×</button>                                              <picture>                  <img class="modal-image js-modal-image" src="/img/1200x675-TS-19609-SEO-TurboPoker_Screenshot_1446113490252_tcm1488-262466.jpg" width="1200" height="675" alt="Turbo Poker" loading="lazy">     </picture>                      </div>                </div>           </div>       </div> </div>   </div>                  </div>                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component">     <div class="text"><div class="rich-text"><p>As a result of the faster blind levels, you could end up short-stacked much sooner than normal. You've got to be able to shove your chips all-in when necessary – and not worry about doing it.</p> <p>Of course, this means that you'll have greater variance in these types of tourneys. and the “<a href="/magazine/strategy/poker-luck">luck factor</a>” will be more of a factor.<br> &nbsp;</p> </div></div> </div></div>   </div>                  </div>             </div>                              </div></div>                 <div class="rich-text">            <div class="rich-text-component">     <div class="text"><h2>Why Play Turbo &amp; Super Turbo Tournaments at 888poker?<br> </h2> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><b>PROS:</b></p> <ul> <li>It takes just a few hours, at the most, to final table these events.</li> <li>If you like your poker fast and furious, this will get your heart racing. You'll be short-stacked sooner, forcing you to play more flips and go all-ins.</li> <li>If you win, you'll make a big hit in a very short amount of time.</li> </ul> <p><b>CONS:</b></p> <ul> <li>These are often very high-variance types of tournaments. Cashing is a bit hit and miss.</li> <li>Winning will be neither here nor there, and nothing like the win rate in some slower tournaments that allow you to play more poker.</li> <li>You can get blinded out very easily soon after the tournament starts, because of the quick blinds.</li> </ul> <h2>Is this Tournament Type for You?</h2> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>If you’re a player who just want to have fun, this tournament type is a perfect. You'll need more luck on your side because you'll be short-stacked earlier, and forced to go all-in more often. Are you the type who just itches to press that the all-in button and watch the cards fly?</p> <p>Also, if you’re short on time, just don’t want to play a long poker session, or have trouble focusing for long periods of time, these tournaments are a great option. They usually only last for a few hours at most, so there's still plenty of time for a round at the cash tables.</p> <h2>Turbo &amp; Super Turbo Tournament Strategy Tips:</h2> <p>&nbsp;</p> <ul> <li><b>Tighten Up Shortly After The Bubble</b>: Once the bubble bursts, players will start to die fast because now they are in the money. Use this time to move up the money ladder by playing slightly <a href="/magazine/strategy/tag-poker-strategy">tighter</a> than normal.</li> <li><b>Be Willing To Take Chances</b>: You’re going to be all-in a bunch of times before the end. You have to be willing to gamble to win the top prize.</li> <li><b>Steal The Blinds</b>: You don’t have to do it with 72-off suit but, because of the fast blind structure, you will need to <a href="/magazine/strategy/daylight-robbery-stealing-blinds">steal blinds</a> to keep your stack healthy.</li> <li><b>Adjust to the Looser Playing Style</b>: Players will be going all-in every hand. Depending on the blind level, and your chip stack you may need to play more (or less) hands.</li> <li><b>Don’t Beat Yourself Up</b>: There’s a lot more luck and variance involved in these types of tournaments, so don’t get down on yourself if you go on a cold streak. When you win, it can turn it all around in the blink of an eye.</li> </ul> <div class="row section"><div><span style="line-height: 25.6px;">Check out some more <a href="/how-to-play-poker/strategy/tournaments/">poker tournament tips</a>.</span></div> <div style="line-height: 25.6px;">&nbsp;</div> </div></div> </div></div>   </div>                  </div>                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="sidebar">            <div class="sidebar-component">          <a href="/poker-tournaments/" class="sidebar-title">Poker Tournaments</a>             <div id="sidebar-menu" class="sidebar-menu js-custom-simplebar custom-simplebar dark-simplebar">                          <div class="sidebar-menu-item">                   <a href="/poker-tournaments/types/knockout/" class="for-item">Knockout</a>               </div>                          <div class="sidebar-menu-item">                   <a href="/poker-tournaments/types/multi-table-tournament/" class="for-item">MTT</a>               </div>                  </div>    </div></div>   </div>                  </div>             </div>                                        </div></div>               </div>      </div> </div></div> <div class="container responsivegrid">  <div class="container-background-color">     <div class="container-wrapper">                             <div id="container-c83a65113b" class="cmp-container">                  <div class="container responsivegrid">  <div class="">     <div class="container-wrapper main-container">                             <div id="container-b7e09586f7" class="cmp-container">                  <div class="article-slider">       <link rel="stylesheet" href="/etc.clientlibs/holdings888/clientlibs/clientlib-swiper.lc-8fbdf4ce96211052d13dbe3c35baf3a9-lc.min.css" type="text/css">                <div class="article-slider-component">     <h3 class="boxTitle h3 text-left">         Related Articles     </h3>      <div class="article-slider-container">         <div class="swiper">             <div class="swiper-wrapper">                                      <div class="swiper-slide">                        